=== 用户体验 ===
各种應用程式通知会按类别分类至不同的组（“渠道”），用户还可暂时延后某則通知<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/14988830/google-android-o-notification-channels-app-categories-control|script-title=en:Android O will give you even more control over notifications|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Gartenberg|first=Chaim|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321195336/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/14988830/google-android-o-notification-channels-app-categories-control|archive-date=2017-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-notification-channels-simplify-managing-notifications/|script-title=en:Android O feature spotlight: Notification Channels give more controls over notifications to users|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Davenport|first=Corbin|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322004311/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-notification-channels-simplify-managing-notifications/|archive-date=2017-03-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。Android Oreo整合了对[[画中画|画中画]]模式的支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/15007754/android-o-developer-preview-picture-in-picture-support|script-title=en:Android O brings picture-in-picture support so you can watch YouTube while hailing a Lyft|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Garun|first=Natt|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321200316/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/15007754/android-o-developer-preview-picture-in-picture-support|archive-date=2017-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-picture-picture-video-devices-new-windowing-features/|script-title=en:Android O feature spotlight: Picture-in-picture video for all devices and new windowing features|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Whitwam|first=Ryan|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322205204/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-picture-picture-video-devices-new-windowing-features/|archive-date=2017-03-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，还简化新增自定义铃声、闹钟声和通知声的过程<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/23/android-o-feature-spotlight-easily-add-custom-ringtones-alarm-sounds-notification-sounds/|script-title=en:Android O feature spotlight: Easily add custom ringtones, alarm sounds, and notification sounds|accessdate=2017-03-24|date=2017-03-23|last=El Khoury|first=Rita|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324023455/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/23/android-o-feature-spotlight-easily-add-custom-ringtones-alarm-sounds-notification-sounds/|archive-date=2017-03-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/23/15042716/android-o-custom-ringtone-notification-sounds-setting|script-title=en:Android O will make it easier to add custom ringtones and notification sounds|accessdate=2017-03-24|date=2017-03-23|last=Statt|first=Nick|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170324000047/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/23/15042716/android-o-custom-ringtone-notification-sounds-setting|archive-date=2017-03-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。“设置”應用程式经过全新设计，主题色改为白色，强化对各项设置的分类<ref name="ars-hands">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/03/hands-on-with-android-o-snooze-that-notification-and-customize-everything/|script-title=en:Hands-on with Android O—A million new settings and an awesome snooze feature|accessdate=2017-04-14|date=2017-03-23|last=Amadeo|first=Ron|publisher=[[Condé_Nast|Condé Nast]]|website=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170414233823/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/03/hands-on-with-android-o-snooze-that-notification-and-customize-everything/|archive-date=2017-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，[[Android_TV|Android TV]]亦有新的主界面<ref>{{cite web|url=https://developer.android.com/preview/api-overview.html#tvlauncher|script-title=en:Android 8.0 Features and APIs - Android Developers|website=developer.android.com|language=en|access-date=2017-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160311235655/http://developer.android.com/preview/api-overview.html#tvlauncher|archive-date=2016-03-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Google声称新版系统从关机状态启动设备所需的时间更短<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.blog.google/products/android/android-oreo-superpowers-coming-device-near-you/|script-title=en:Android Oreo superpowers, coming to a device near you|date=2017-08-21|newspaper=Google|accessdate=2017-08-22|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822013223/https://www.blog.google/products/android/android-oreo-superpowers-coming-device-near-you/|archive-date=2017-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，以及透過限制背景應用程式延長电池可用时间<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.techadvisor.co.uk/new-product/google-android/android-oreo-news-release-date-new-features-3647595/|script-title=en:Android 8.0 Oreo officially unveiled|last=Black|first=Marie|newspaper=Tech Advisor|accessdate=2017-08-22|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170821230159/http://www.techadvisor.co.uk/new-product/google-android/android-oreo-news-release-date-new-features-3647595/|archive-date=2017-08-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

=== 平台 ===
Android Oreo新增对[[Wi-Fi|Wi-Fi]]的[[Wi-Fi联盟|Wi-Fi Aware]]基础上周边感知联网（NAN）规范<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-neighborhood-aware-networking-nan-mode-wifi/|script-title=en:Android O feature spotlight: Neighborhood Aware Networking (NAN) mode for WiFi|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Whitwam|first=Ryan|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322204637/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-feature-spotlight-neighborhood-aware-networking-nan-mode-wifi/|archive-date=2017-03-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>和应用内宽[[色域|色域]]的支持<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/feature-spotlight-android-o-will-support-wide-color-gamut-profiles-in-apps-for-capable-displays/|script-title=en:Android O feature spotlight: Android will support wide color gamut profiles in apps|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Ruddock|first=David|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322204613/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/feature-spotlight-android-o-will-support-wide-color-gamut-profiles-in-apps-for-capable-displays/|archive-date=2017-03-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>，提供[[应用程序接口|API]]供{{tsl|en|Autofill|自动填充|自动填写程序}}使用，使WebView支持多-{zh-hans:进程;zh-hant:程序}-和{{tsl|en|Google Safe Browsing|Google安全浏览}}功能，允许[[網際協議通話技術|VoIP]]应用使用新增的API集成至系统层面，支持应用功能在远程显示设备上启动<ref name="First developer preview"/>。[[Android_Runtime|Android Runtime]]（ART）性能获得改进<ref name="First developer preview"/>，缓存处理能力增强<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://theleaker.com/android-o-8-0-update-smartphones-list/|script-title=en:List of smartphones to receive the Android O 8.0 Oreo Update|date=2017-07-26|work=The Leaker|language=en|access-date=2017-07-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170822013913/https://theleaker.com/android-o-8-0-update-smartphones-list/|archive-date=2017-08-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Android Oreo对后台应用活动施以更多限制，借此提升电池使用时间<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/14988222/android-o-app-background-run|script-title=en:Android Oreo will limit what apps can do in the background to save battery life|accessdate=2017-03-22|date=2017-03-21|last=Carman|first=Ashley|publisher=[[Vox_Media|Vox Media]]|website=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170321202922/http://www.theverge.com/2017/3/21/14988222/android-o-app-background-run|archive-date=2017-03-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。应用可选用“适应性图标”以支持各种主题下不同的图标形状要求，如圆形、方形和[[方圓形|圆角矩形]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-developer-preview-feature-spotlight-adaptive-icons-give-devs-and-oems-easy-shape-masks-extra-effects/|script-title=en:Android O Feature Spotlight: Adaptive icons give devs and OEMs easy shape masks, extra effects|accessdate=2017-03-21|date=2017-03-21|last=Crider|first=Michael|website=Android Police|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170322204602/http://www.androidpolice.com/2017/03/21/android-o-developer-preview-feature-spotlight-adaptive-icons-give-devs-and-oems-easy-shape-masks-extra-effects/|archive-date=2017-03-22|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

Android Oreo中新增数十个新[[繪文字|绘文字]]，这些绘文字将被纳入[[Unicode|Unicode]] 10标准。系统将使用重新设计的新绘文字字体，各绘文字的面部均改为传统的圆形，抛弃自[[Android_4.4|Android 4.4]]以来一直采用的“blob”设计。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gsmarena.com/google_redesigns_emoji_again_for_android_o-news-25103.php|script-title=en:Google redesigns emoji (again) for Android O|accessdate=2017-05-19|website=GSMArena|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518230839/http://www.gsmarena.com/google_redesigns_emoji_again_for_android_o-news-25103.php|archive-date=2017-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/google-io-2017-android-o-emoji-5-0-revamp-blob-design-killed-1695244|script-title=en:Google I/O 2017: Android O to Bring Redesigned Emojis, Full Support for Emoji 5.0 Characters|accessdate=2017-05-19|website=NDTV|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518114952/http://gadgets.ndtv.com/mobiles/news/google-io-2017-android-o-emoji-5-0-revamp-blob-design-killed-1695244|archive-date=2017-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>

此次更新修订了Android底层架构，支持设备硬件工作所用的底层厂商代码将通过一个称为“供应商接口”的[[硬體抽象層|硬件抽象层]]与Android操作系统框架分离，供应商接口需与Android未来版本保持[[向前兼容|向前兼容]]。理论上来说，为设备提供Android的新版本更新时，设备厂商只需对系统框架和预装应用做出必要修改，供应商接口将保持不变，此项技术被称为“Project Treble”。<ref name="ars-treble">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/google-hopes-to-fix-android-updates-no-really-with-project-treble/|script-title=en:Google’s "Project Treble" solves one of Android’s many update roadblocks|accessdate=2017-05-12|website=Ars Technica|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171203010312/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/google-hopes-to-fix-android-updates-no-really-with-project-treble/|archive-date=2017-12-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>Android Nougat引入的“无缝更新”概念亦获调整，下载更新文件时现可跳过用户分区而直接下载至系统分区，减轻系统更新对存储空间的需求<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/08/android-8-0s-streaming-os-updates-will-work-even-if-your-phone-is-full/|script-title=en:Android 8.0’s "streaming OS updates" will work even if your phone is full|work=Ars Technica|language=en|access-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807143807/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/08/android-8-0s-streaming-os-updates-will-work-even-if-your-phone-is-full/|archive-date=2017-08-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

系统为内存不超过1GB的所有低阶设备提供Android Go特别版本。这些设备出厂时的平台优化可减少数据流量使用（包括默认启用流量节省模式），还将搭载资源和带宽消耗更少的特别版[[Google流動服務|Google移动服务]]（如YouTube Go）。[[Google_Play|Google Play商店]]亦会突显出适合这些设备使用的轻量级应用。<ref name="ars-androidgo">{{cite web|url=https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/android-go-will-strip-android-down-for-ultra-low-budget-phones/|script-title=en:"Android Go" will strip Android down for ultra-low-budget phones|accessdate=2017-05-19|publisher=Conde Nast|website=Ars Technica|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170518231714/https://arstechnica.com/gadgets/2017/05/android-go-will-strip-android-down-for-ultra-low-budget-phones/|archive-date=2017-05-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="engadget-androidgo">{{cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/18/android-go-could-help-make-android-o-a-runaway-success/|script-title=en:Android Go could help make Android O a runaway success|accessdate=2017-05-19|website=Engadget|language=en|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170519135747/https://www.engadget.com/2017/05/18/android-go-could-help-make-android-o-a-runaway-success/|archive-date=2017-05-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== Android Go ===
Android Oreo（Go Edition）就是針對低階規格、連線受限的用戶而設，主要適用於[[隨機存取記憶體|隨機存取記憶體]]容量為512MB至1GB的行動裝置，為了配合無法使用大量數據的用戶，系統有更清晰的數據用量提示和管理，亦會在預載的Google Apps，例如Chrome瀏覽器、YouTube等提供預設節約數據功能。

